      • grow

        private void grow()
        Increases the capacity of the list of students by doubling the size underlying array. Calls Array constructor to create a new list and then iterate over each element in the old array to copy into the new array.

      • remove

        public void remove​(Student student)
        Removes student from list. Iterates over list to find the specified student to remove. Continues iterating through the rest of the list to move each element back one index so that the underlying array's size always represents the index to add a new student.
        Parameters:
        student - Student to remove from list
